{"tid":1183834,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"奇蹟童顏 透明感日本女演員扮4歲幼兒生毫無違和感","createTime":"2019-06-03T08:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T09:01:00.000Z","uid":221236,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9f40459e64dc515504735988513cfe9ad316f7","tid":1183834,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"37歲的日本知名女演員安達祐實在演藝圈一直有著「不老童顏」的稱號， 12 歲時就以童星身份出道的她，當年就以日劇《無家可歸的小孩》走紅，穿著水手服、綁著雙馬尾的造型成為了安達祐實的經典螢幕形象。不過對於身高僅 153 公分的她，身形嬌小加上保養得宜的苗條身材和娃娃臉，讓安達祐實一直被稱為是「奇蹟童顏」女星。為了驗證安達祐實的「奇蹟童顏」、「扮演任何年下歲數角色都不會有違和感」的江湖傳說，知名談話節目《閒聊 007》就準備了各個年齡層的服裝讓安達祐實穿上，沒想到實驗結果更是讓眾多日本網友感到吃驚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZRx2uY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZRx2uY.png&h=1b724782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DB2pTBE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDB2pTBE.png&h=8a31db9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acW2FgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacW2FgG.png&h=3ad37529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 15 歲國中生的水手服<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuMidzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuMidzC.jpg&h=b26acd88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjujHtR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjujHtR.jpg&h=aee29664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 4 歲幼稚園服裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74UWKGr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74UWKGr.jpg&h=9be43cda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cda9ab0af1f7eddfd9292f278c3621e62ed30499","tid":1183834,"uid":52068,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"個樣係靚，但睇得出上咗年紀"},{"pid":"2300a7bb3a2a88616533849ce58812c888d93c6a","tid":1183834,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:44:45.000Z","